com.pkware.smartcrypt.keymanagement.smartkeys

Class ErrorSmartkey

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.pkware.smartcrypt.keymanagement.smartkeys.ErrorSmartkey
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Smartkey

    public final class ErrorSmartkey
extends Object
implements Smartkey
    Indicates that an error occurred while loading a Smartkey. Used in an observable stream to avoid breaking the stream. Developers should already be coding to handle scenarios such as no decryption key, not being allowed to encrypt, etc.
    See Also:
    to further investigate the error
